                    <span>Linux is awesome but...I've been thinking about adding a BSD system for my home.edu. I'm convinced it will be a great experience. The author's passion for BSD is evident. Thanks, Mr. Lehey.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">AWESOME FreeBSD Resource</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
